sequenceDiagram
    participant App as Application
    participant Provider as EmbeddingProvider
    participant Client as Client (e.g., openai.Client)
    participant HTTP as http.Client
    participant API as Provider API

    Note over App,API: Single Embedding Flow

    App->>Provider: Embed(ctx, "text")
    Provider->>Client: Embed(ctx, "text")
    Client->>Client: EmbedBatch(ctx, ["text"])
    Client->>Client: Marshal embedRequest to JSON
    Client->>HTTP: NewRequestWithContext(POST, url, body)
    Client->>HTTP: Set Authorization header
    HTTP->>API: POST /embeddings
    API-->>HTTP: 200 OK + embedResponse JSON
    HTTP-->>Client: *http.Response
    Client->>Client: Decode JSON response
    Client->>Client: Extract embedding by index
    Client-->>Provider: ([]float32, nil)
    Provider-->>App: ([]float32, nil)

    Note over App,API: Batch Embedding Flow

    App->>Provider: EmbedBatch(ctx, ["text1", "text2", "text3"])
    Provider->>Client: EmbedBatch(ctx, ["text1", "text2", "text3"])
    Client->>Client: Marshal embedRequest to JSON
    Client->>HTTP: NewRequestWithContext(POST, url, body)
    Client->>HTTP: Set Authorization header
    HTTP->>API: POST /embeddings
    API-->>HTTP: 200 OK + embedResponse JSON
    HTTP-->>Client: *http.Response
    Client->>Client: Decode JSON response
    Client->>Client: Reorder embeddings by index
    Client-->>Provider: ([][]float32, nil)
    Provider-->>App: ([][]float32, nil)

    Note over App,API: Error Flow

    App->>Provider: Embed(ctx, "text")
    Provider->>Client: Embed(ctx, "text")
    Client->>Client: EmbedBatch(ctx, ["text"])
    Client->>HTTP: POST request
    HTTP->>API: POST /embeddings
    API-->>HTTP: 429 Too Many Requests
    HTTP-->>Client: *http.Response (status 429)
    Client->>Client: Read error body
    Client-->>Provider: (nil, "provider: API error 429 - ...")
    Provider-->>App: (nil, error)

    Note over App,API: Bedrock Titan Batch Flow (Sequential)

    App->>Provider: EmbedBatch(ctx, ["text1", "text2"])
    Provider->>Client: EmbedBatch(ctx, ["text1", "text2"])
    Client->>Client: Detect amazon.titan prefix
    loop For each text
        Client->>Client: embedTitan(ctx, text)
        Client->>Client: Marshal titanRequest
        Client->>Client: signRequest (AWS SigV4)
        Client->>HTTP: POST /model/{model}/invoke
        HTTP->>API: Signed request
        API-->>HTTP: 200 OK + titanResponse
        HTTP-->>Client: titanResponse
        Client->>Client: Extract embedding
    end
    Client-->>Provider: ([][]float32, nil)
    Provider-->>App: ([][]float32, nil)
